界面新闻。
Interface news.
界面新闻是中国具有影响力的原创财经新媒体，只服务于独立思考的人群。
Interface News is an original and influential new financial media in China, serving only the people who think independently.
对于日本国内的疫情，久未发声的软银集团掌舵人孙正义坐不住了，时隔三年他再发推特，表示愿意为抗击疫情提供帮助，首批将捐赠100万份简易PCR病毒检测试剂。
Japan's domestic epidemic, the long-silent soft silver group pilot Sun justice, after three years he sent Twitter, offering to help fight the epidemic, the first will donate 1 million simple PCR virus detection reagents.
结果，这番“好意”遭到了大量网友的反对，人们留言认为这样做完全是在“捣乱”，会让大量患者涌至医院，从而造成日本医疗的系统崩溃。
As a result, the move was met with a barrage of netizens, who suggested it would be "disruptive," flooding hospitals with patients and causing a collapse of Japan's health-care system.
2小时后，孙正义“认输”了，他在推特写道：“听说有很多人即使想检查也得不到检查，我才提议的，但评价这么差，要不算了吧……”今年63岁的孙正义出生于日本，1981年创建软件银行集团，2014年因参与投资的阿里巴巴登陆美股市场，孙正义的财富净值涨至166亿美元，跻身日本首富。
Two hours later, Sun "conceded," he wrote in a tweet. "I heard there were a lot of people who didn't get checked even if they wanted to check, but that wasn't the case..." Sun, 63, was born in Japan, founded the software banking group in 1981 and became Japan's richest man when Alibaba landed in the US stock market in 2014
2019年3月，孙正义以216亿美元财富排名2019年福布斯全球亿万富豪榜第43位，日本第2位，仅次于柳井正（优衣库）。
In March 2019, Sun was ranked 43rd on the Forbes list of the world's billionaires for $21.6 billion, and second only to Yanai (Uniqlo).
